  "detailed_description": "As a manager of an hospital near bankrupt, you find that a brick on the head will give you patients. Throw objects in the streets along four worlds with levels full of madness and fun. Also play on <strong>Hospital Mode</strong> where you can build your own hospital, take care of patients, protect him with security guards...<br><br><strong>Pick carefully your items for every level, there a lot ways to play!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2592000/extras/8b4367b4573af25a006194eaacc12fc3.poster.avif?t=1704651449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2592000/extras/8b4367b4573af25a006194eaacc12fc3.webm?t=1704651449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2592000/extras/8b4367b4573af25a006194eaacc12fc3.mp4?t=1704651449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Different types of Enemies and Allies!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2592000/extras/74ee2b2a6b800a3801f6d4f34fcebd62.poster.avif?t=1704651449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2592000/extras/74ee2b2a6b800a3801f6d4f34fcebd62.webm?t=1704651449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2592000/extras/74ee2b2a6b800a3801f6d4f34fcebd62.mp4?t=1704651449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Build your own hospital in \"Hospital Mode\"!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2592000/extras/2f3ddde63e75f4173266dcc9873eae38.poster.avif?t=1704651449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2592000/extras/2f3ddde63e75f4173266dcc9873eae38.webm?t=1704651449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2592000/extras/2f3ddde63e75f4173266dcc9873eae38.mp4?t=1704651449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Take care of your patients in fun minigames and protect your hospital!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2592000/extras/c805cbb763cc70619f54db671c7b5f02.poster.avif?t=1704651449\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2592000/extras/c805cbb763cc70619f54db671c7b5f02.webm?t=1704651449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2592000/extras/c805cbb763cc70619f54db671c7b5f02.mp4?t=1704651449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Adventure Mode</strong>, with four worlds.<br></li><li><strong>Endless Mode</strong>, personalize your games selecting how often spawns your allies and enemies.<br></li><li><strong>Hospital Mode</strong>, build your own Hospital, clean it, heal patients in fun minigames, protect him with security guards, talk with sanity inspectors...</li></ul>",
